# NOTE: several runtime state files above are gitignored. For the GitHub
# Actions deploy, state is persisted on a SEPARATE `state` branch (not main),
# so these ignores on main are intentional and correct — see deploy plan.

# --- Large / vendored / irrelevant to the cloud deploy (added 2026-07-21) ---
# Core trading modules do NOT import any of these; keep them out of the repo.
# (inline comments are NOT allowed after a pattern in .gitignore — keep them
#  on their own lines like this)
# Models/            = 13 GB of local model files — never commit
# TradingAgents/     = 290 MB vendored project with its OWN .git
# financial-services/= separate project with its OWN .git
# ui_test_agent/     = 22 MB local UI-test tooling, not needed on cloud
# lstm_models/       = 197 MB trained models — CI retrains missing ones
Models/
TradingAgents/
financial-services/
ui_test_agent/
lstm_models/
.codex/
.playwright-mcp/
.yfinance_cache/

